			President Ma Ying-jeou of Taiwan defended his decision to meet with President Xi Jinping of China, rejecting accusations that he had undermined Taiwan&#8217;s sovereignty. <a href="//sinosphere.blogs.nytimes.com/2015/11/13/taiwan-china-ma-ying-jeou-xi-jinping/" class="more-link">Read&#160;more&#8230;</a></p>
